<h2 id="either-or-nither-nor">Either or Nither nor</h2>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="err">!</span> <span class="o">/</span><span class="n">usr</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="nb">bin</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">env</span> <span class="n">python</span>

<span class="n">flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"</span>
<span class="n">enc_flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">91</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">241</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">101</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">166</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">85</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">192</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">87</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">188</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">110</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">164</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">99</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">152</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">98</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">252</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">34</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">152</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">117</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">164</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">99</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">162</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">107</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="n">key</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">KEY_LEN</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">4</span>

<span class="c1"># Encrypt the flag
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">idx</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">c</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nf">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">flag</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">enc_flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nf">ord</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">idx</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="nf">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">)]</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>enc_flag 부분이 python code가 잘못되어있는데..</p>

<p>암튼</p>

<p>문제에서 FLAG 형식이 MetaCTF{}라고 하여서 원문을 알고 있기 때문에</p>

<p>XOR의 self-inverse 속성을 이용한다.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">#! /usr/bin/env python
</span>
<span class="n">flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"</span>
<span class="n">enc_flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">91</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">241</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">101</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">166</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">85</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">192</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">87</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">188</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">110</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">164</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">99</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">152</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">98</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">252</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">34</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">152</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">117</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">164</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">99</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">162</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">107</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="n">key</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">22</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">148</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">17</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">199</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">KEY_LEN</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">4</span>

<span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">enc_flag</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># Encrypt the flag
#for idx, c in enumerate(flag):
#    enc_flag = ord(c) ^ key[idx % len(key)]
</span><span class="n">res</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">''</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">idx</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">c</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nf">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">enc_flag</span><span class="p">):</span>
	<span class="n">res</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="nf">chr</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">^</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">idx</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="n">KEY_LEN</span><span class="p">])</span>

<span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">res</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1">#print(enc_flag[0] ^ ord('M'))
#print(enc_flag[1] ^ ord('e'))
#print(enc_flag[2] ^ ord('t'))
#print(enc_flag[3] ^ ord('a'))
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>Meta를 xor한 값을 출력하고 키에 넣어서 복호화를 시도한다.</p>

<p>MetaCTF{x0r_th3_c0re}</p>

<h2 id="a-fine-cipher">A Fine Cipher</h2>
<p>암호문이 주어진다. <br />
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">JSNRZHIVJUCVIVFCVYBMVBDRZCXRIVBINCORBCSFHCBINOCRMHBD</code></p>

<p><a href="https://www.dcode.fr/cipher-identifier">https://www.dcode.fr/cipher-identifier</a></p>

<p>제목에 힌트가 있을거 같아서 보니 affine cipher가 떠올랐다. (최근 인코그니토 CTF에서 풂)</p>

